OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781273476
OL,3,CRare dormice reintroduced into woods
OL,4,Cto help revive species
OL,6,FMore than 40 rare hazel dormice have
OL,7,Fbeen released into ancient woodland in
OL,8,FLeicestershire to boost efforts to
OL,9,Fbring the tiny mammals back to the
OL,10,Fcounty.
OL,12,FThe reintroduction on the Bradgate
OL,13,FPark Trust estate is part of ongoing
OL,14,Fnational efforts by the People's Trust
OL,15,Ffor Endangered Species (PTES) to save
OL,16,Fdormice, which have declined by more
OL,17,Fthan 70% nationally since 2000, from
OL,18,Fextinction.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
