PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781273476
OL,3,CRare dormice reintroduced into woods
OL,4,Cto help revive species
OL,6,FThe dormice have been bred in
OL,7,Fcaptivity by partner organisations as
OL,8,Fpart of the reintroduction programme,
OL,9,Fwith most of this year's animals
OL,10,Fprovided by Wildwood Trust following
OL,11,Fits most successful breeding season to
OL,12,Fdate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781273476
OL,3,CRare dormice reintroduced into woods
OL,4,Cto help revive species
OL,6,FAll animals have been given a full
OL,7,Fhealth check and quarantined for four
OL,8,Fweeks to ensure they are healthy and
OL,9,Fdo not carry any disease, before being
OL,10,Freleased in pairs into nest boxes
OL,11,Fplaced inside large mesh enclosures
OL,12,Fwith natural light, foliage and new
OL,13,Ffood and water daily, to help them
OL,14,Facclimatise to the wood.
OL,16,FAfter 10 days, following a final
OL,17,Fhealth check, the cage doors will be
OL,18,Fopened, and they will be free to
OL,19,Fexplore the woodland.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
