FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1781273476
OL,3,CRare dormice reintroduced into woods
OL,4,Cto help revive species
OL,6,FThe reintroduction programme has seen
OL,7,F1,163 dormice released into 27
OL,8,Fdifferent woodlands in 14 counties
OL,9,Facross Britain since it began in 1993,
OL,10,FPTES said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
